About

I’m Juliana, Founder of GTA Microblading. I’ve been meticulously sculpting brows for over 20 years—but that’s not the whole story. I grew up in a beauty salon. I started my career sweeping in my family’s shop at the age of 12. I watched masterful practitioners and soaked up their expertise every chance I got. By 16, I had a deep appreciation for cosmetology and my own clientele. My last name, Trichilo, derives from the Greek word ‘trichos’, meaning ‘hair’. I was trained to wield a brush and a blade. I was raised to accentuate and celebrate beauty.

It’s not just my history. It’s my destiny.

Reviews

Our clients say it best.

"I was tired of drawing on my brows just to leave the house. I was desperate for brows I could wear proudly. And, yes, I wanted a no maintenance solution too. Juliana, you gave me everything I could have asked for... and more!"
Anila
Brow Shaping & Virtual Brow Lift
"Ask anyone and they'll tell you, Enza is the most vibrant person I know! I wanted eyebrows that are vibrant too. Juliana took the time to understand me and my skin. Now, my brows match the rest of me. I regularly send Juliana new clients. She earned it. "
Enza
Combination Brows
